column1: Table 18 (a)-Estimated resident population by age group and sex - Island of Mauritius, 1984 - 2016
(i) Figures from 1984 to 1989 are based on the 1983 population  census  and figures from 1991 to 1999 are based on the 1990 population census.
These figures will be different from table 1(a) as population by age group was not revised for these years
(iii) Figures from 2001 to 2015 have been revised  based on the 2011 population  census
